{"tid":2279173,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"有冇人覺得christopher chak + 林夕好撚屈","createTime":"2020-11-09T14:58:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T12:03:39.000Z","uid":138802,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"cb6da25800898b7f4107cd4c86a936ac6d799463","tid":2279173,"uid":138802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T14:58:00.000Z","msg":"唔識音樂<br />\n但佢每首都差唔多四分半鐘<br />\n唔長唔短岩岩好  夠時間比你投入<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾鍾意呢d「長氣」，好多歌詞嘅歌<br />\n亦都好鍾意佢果種密集式旋律<br />\n聽落一定唔會令你好傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但又會好空虛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，適合me time聽嘅音樂<br />\n呢種到喉唔到肺嘅感覺...<br />\n簡直冇對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知有冇同好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"871bdf8fd340e9697f5067813800ed1557137f10","tid":2279173,"uid":36040,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T15:42:45.000Z","msg":"例如有咩歌?"},{"pid":"ea5d56ec1c534246965f2f6ba7076f3d04afb56b","tid":2279173,"uid":138802,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"871bdf8fd340e9697f5067813800ed1557137f10","tid":2279173,"uid":36040,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T15:42:45.000Z","msg":"例如有咩歌?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-09T15:50:19.000Z","msg":"以下係睇wiki<br />\n<br />\n佢當年參賽作品就係富士山下，之後就比左eason<br />\n(你要諗下佢果陣係冇人識，但第一首已經有夕爺寫詞再比當時嘅天王級歌手)<br />\n<br />\n跟住再寫左鍾無艷，係當時又係紅到爆嘅謝安琪<br />\n仲有張敬軒嘅塵埃落定，不吐不快咁  旋律都好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭兩首我覺得係巔峰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽旋律都會聽到喊嘅歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後果d歌嘅曲風我就冇咁鍾意<br />\n不過都好有寂寞/委屈嘅味道"},{"pid":"f024bd366d7492771a2af540cdb7f4aa2b1c7add","tid":2279173,"uid":36040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea5d56ec1c534246965f2f6